    <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="classHoverState" kindref="compound">HoverState</ref> - Mouse hover state management. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Tracks hover state for a component and provides callbacks for state changes. Handles mouse cursor changes and hover-based styling.</para>
<para>Usage: class MyComponent : public juce::Component { <ref refid="classHoverState" kindref="compound">HoverState</ref> hoverState;</para>
<para>MyComponent() { hoverState.onHoverChanged = [this](bool h) { repaint(); }; }</para>
<para>void mouseEnter(const juce::MouseEvent&amp;) override { hoverState.setHovered(true); } void mouseExit(const juce::MouseEvent&amp;) override { hoverState.setHovered(false); }</para>
<para>void paint(juce::Graphics&amp; g) override { g.setColour(hoverState.isHovered() ? hoverColor : normalColor); } }; </para>
    </detaileddescription>
